text: Batwheels is an American computer-animated superhero children's television series that premiered on September 17, 2022, on HBO Max, and on October 17, 2022, on Cartoon Network's preschool block, Cartoonito and June 18, 2024 on NETFLIX. ==References== Category:2020s American animated television series Category:2020s American children's television series Category:2022 American television series debuts Category:Action television series Category:Cartoon Network series Category:Cartoonito Category:English-language television programs Category:HBO Max original programming
